\cf0 Founding\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa298\partightenfactor0

\f1\b\fs36 \cf0 Built on energy and trust\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 Absolute Window Cleaning and Pressure Washing was born from the goal to bring connection, energy, and youthfulness to the St. Louis home service industry.\
After successfully operating a previous exterior cleaning partnership (started summer of 2023), I realized that STL Homeowners needed a company that combined energetic service with the reliability of an insured business. I went back to scratch to build Absolute, and here we are!\
Our mission beyond the work\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa298\partightenfactor0

\f1\b\fs36 \cf0 Supporting students\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 As an architecture student, I love my job even more because it allows me to learn even more about the homes I'll hopefully design someday.\
That being said, I am a student! Supporting Absolute means supporting three students in continuing higher education, and we're forever grateful.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
