\f1\b\fs36 \cf0 \strokec3 Questions about us\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 Everything you need to know about our service, standards, and what makes us different.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

\f1\b\fs28 \cf0 How long have you been doing this?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 We've been in the exterior cleaning business since summer of 2023, and Absolute was created a year later.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

\f1\b\fs28 \cf0 Where is my money going when I hire you?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 10% of all profits go back to the community through homeless outreach. We make and keep ziploc bags in the car with materials to immediately help anyone we see on the street, and the rest of that money goes to help buy things for food and clothing drives in our community.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

\f1\b\fs28 \cf0 Why should I hire students?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 When you hire Absolute, you're hiring a team who makes you the main priority. Because we're not as big as some of our competitors, we won't be taking other work calls while on the job, or shifting your job around on the schedule to accommodate other clients.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

\f1\b\fs28 \cf0 Can I let my dog out to say hi when you do the walkaround?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 Uh, of course! If it was up to us, dogs would be out the entire time we work, but unfortunately turning a black lab into a golden retriever might not be what you had in mind when scheduling a cleaning.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

\f1\b\fs28 \cf0 What happens if something goes wrong during a job?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 We're humans, not robots. If we miss a spot or a screen doesn't quite sit right, just tell us! We won't get defensive; we'll get it fixed. Our reputation is worth way more than saving 10 minutes.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
